name: Element_expectFirstTest
description: Unit tests for the 'expectFirst' method of the Element class in Jsoup.

test_cases.name: testExpectFirstWithMatchingElement
test_cases.description: Tests the 'expectFirst' method with a matching element, ensuring it returns the correct element and its text.

test_cases.name: testExpectFirstWithNoMatchingElement
test_cases.description: Tests the 'expectFirst' method with no matching element, ensuring it throws a ValidationException.
